{"tha-ap347:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap347:0.2":"Ekapadumiyavagga ","tha-ap347:0.3":"Nalagarikattheraapadana ","tha-ap347:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap347:1.2":"harito nama pabbato; ","tha-ap347:1.3":"Sayambhu narado nama, ","tha-ap347:1.4":"rukkhamule vasi tada. ","tha-ap347:2.1":"Nalagaram karitvana, ","tha-ap347:2.2":"tinena chadayim aham; ","tha-ap347:2.3":"Cankamam sodhayitvana, ","tha-ap347:2.4":"sayambhussa adasaham. ","tha-ap347:3.1":"Catuddasasu kappesu, ","tha-ap347:3.2":"devaloke ramim aham; ","tha-ap347:3.3":"Catusattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap347:3.4":"devarajjam akarayim. ","tha-ap347:4.1":"Catusattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap347:4.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap347:4.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap347:4.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap347:5.1":"Ubbiddham bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap347:5.2":"Indalatthiva uggatam; ","tha-ap347:5.3":"Sahassathambham atulam, ","tha-ap347:5.4":"Vimanam sapabhassaram. ","tha-ap347:6.1":"Dve sampatti anubhotva, ","tha-ap347:6.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap347:6.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap347:6.4":"sasane pabbajim aham. ","tha-ap347:7.1":"Padhanapahitattomhi, ","tha-ap347:7.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap347:7.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap347:7.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap347:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap347:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap347:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap347:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nalagariko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap347:10.1":"Nalagarikattherassapadanam pancamam. "}